Responsible, sustainable miningand giving back to communities. These are the tenets of Eurasian Resources Group’s (ERG) mining operations in the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC). CEO BENEDIKT SOBOTKA speaks to GERARD PETER about the company’s efforts in contributing to a low carbon economy and uplifting mining communities in the country. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 4, 2019 and will be published in full on 15 May 2019 You can read the
